## Summary of Iteration 3 Optimizations

### Bottleneck Analysis
From iteration 2 results, the performance bottleneck was clear:
- **lineitem_aggregation_filter: 2676.91 ms (69.7% of total)** ← DOMINANT
- result_aggregation: 859.41 ms (22.4%)
